1. Design a game for children , which prints a singular word from a predefined list and asks the user to enter the plural of the word. Check if the answer is correct and display "Good","Correct","Wrong" etc based on the answer. (10 Marks)

2. Using TextBlob ,

(i). Read the contents of a file. List the sentences in file.

(ii). Read an integer (n) fom the keyboard and display the nth sentence and nth word in the file. (10 Marks) 